metadata.name: #1: Swoopy Boiz
metadata.description:
First of September rolls along and the boiz roll out of every half-built nest with their peckers sharpened. Too late for taxes now, because youse bettabelieve there’ll be blood. Homes weren’t built in a day, so prep your homemade eyes-painted-on ice-cream tub helmets and antenna extensions for a full season of swoops. This is their time, not ours.

---

Artwork & Design by Ben Toupein
https://planetaustralia.art

Also available in limited-edition physical format via the Brown Cardigan Shop: https://shop.browncardigan.com/collections/planet-australia.
